\#Problem 1 ( To find second largest integer)



Converted the list into a set to remove duplicate values and sorted it in descending order.

Returned the second element from the sorted list as the second largest number.



\#Problem 2



Removed spaces and special characters and converted the string to lowercase for uniform comparison.

