\# Problem 3



Split the text into words and counted the frequency of each word using a dictionary.

Returned the word with the highest frequency, choosing the lexicographically smaller one in case of a tie.





\## Problem 4

Used nested loops to check every possible pair of elements in the array.

Stored the pairs whose sum matched the target value while avoiding duplicate pairs.





